message.body: My, my, I have gotten myself into a problem!
Exes colluding against one another, against me, spectacles, public and private, high emotions, emotions dissipating, kisses hello, angry sex. Ugh, goodbye holidays, i retreat.
I did have wonderful food on Christmas, all day, but with a tremendous price. I got a new expedition jacket, and for no reason because I want to move to Southeast Asia. I got the receipt.
I want to hear all of the gory details. We could build a house in Cambodia for the price of the jacket
